description: When it comes to the best coffee in the Bay Area, you can bet that Hedge Coffee is brewing it up at their badass bar. You can find this cool crew popping up all around San Fran, at all the coolest events in town. All of their drinks are of utmost quality and exclusively made with local products, so just one sip will send you on one deliciously caffeinated trip. For espresso-based beverages, nitro cold brew, and manually brewed coffees with a delectable edge, be sure to head straight to Hedge.
name: Hedge Coffee
